  <brief_title>I-BiT - Evaluation of a Novel Binocular Treatment System (I-BiTTM) in Children With Amblyopia</brief_title>
  <acronym>I-BiT</acronym>
  <official_title>Evaluation and Development of a Novel Binocular Treatment (I-BiTTM) System Using Video Clips and Interactive Games to Improve Vision in Children With Amblyopia ('Lazy Eye').</official_title>
